    "plan_content": "Here's a summary of the complete plan:\n\n---\n\n## Stepper Component — Implementation Plan\n\n### What gets created (5 new files)\n\n| Layer | File |\n|-------|------|\n| Base (radix) | `registry/bases/radix/ui/stepper.tsx` — abstract, `cn-*` tokens, `IconPlaceholder` |\n| Base (base-ui) | `registry/bases/base/ui/stepper.tsx` — identical, just different `lib/utils` import path |\n| Styled | `registry/new-york-v4/ui/stepper.tsx` — concrete Tailwind classes + `lucide-react` |\n| Radix example | `registry/bases/radix/examples/stepper-example.tsx` — 5 sub-variants |\n| ny-v4 demo | `registry/new-york-v4/examples/stepper-demo.tsx` — minimal controlled demo |\n\n### What gets appended (5 registry entries, no existing files modified)\nAll `stepper` entries inserted **alphabetically between `spinner` and `switch`** in each `_registry.ts`.\n\n### Architecture decisions\n- **Follows the Carousel pattern** — pure React, two custom contexts (`StepperContext` + `StepperItemContext`), no Radix/base-ui primitive\n- **`StepperSeparator`** is a sibling *between* `<StepperItem>` elements (like `BreadcrumbSeparator`); reads `orientation` from context → `h-px flex-1 mt-4` (horizontal) or `w-px h-6 ml-4` (vertical)\n- **`StepperContent`** is a child *inside* `<StepperItem>`; returns `null` when its step isn't active\n- **Step state** (`active` / `completed` / `pending`) is computed from `value` comparison + explicit `completed` prop on `<StepperItem>`\n- **Controlled + uncontrolled** both supported via `value` / `defaultValue` / `onValueChange`\n- `data-slot`, `data-state`, `data-orientation`, `data-disabled` on every element\n\n### Sub-components\n`Stepper`, `StepperItem`, `StepperTrigger`, `StepperIndicator`, `StepperTitle`, `StepperDescription`, `StepperSeparator`, `StepperContent` + exported `useStepper` / `useStepperItem` hooks",
